TEXT.S: Qowgan Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Syorinsyang ka alang Qowgan. 449 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,385 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 93% niqan 1,284 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 7% niqan 101 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Truku76%, Amis 6%, Tayal 4%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, Bunun 1%, ni rahuq na o 6%.
